#

Pasta Primavera

35 min
$12
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow Fat

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Quick MealVegetarianPasta

Description

A vibrant and colorful pasta dish loaded with fresh vegetables, perfect for a light and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • pasta (your choice): 8 oz.
  • bell peppers (mixed colors): 1 cup, sliced
  • zucchini: 1 medium, sliced
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • carrots: 1 medium, julienned
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • fresh basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
